<div class="span12">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="hero-unit">
			<h1>A Call To Arms: Star Fleet</h1>
			<h2>Fleet Calculator and Ship Database</h2>
			<p>Please <%= link_to "sign up", signup_path %> for an account or if you are already a member please <%= link_to "sign in", signin_path %>.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="span3 offset1">
			<h3>Build It!</h3>
			<p>Use the Fleet calculator to design your fleet simply by clicking the add to fleet button.  Your fleet list will appear on the right side of the screen.  You can add or remove ships from your list until you have your fleet optimized.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="span3">
			<h3>View It!</h3>
			<p>Once you have finished assigning ships to your fleet you can review each of the ship data sheets by clicking view.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="span3">
			<h3>Print It!</h3>
			<p>While viewing the ship diagram you can print a printer friendly ship data card with play aids to keep track of your shields, hull, and critical score for each row of the critical hits table.  Good luck, commander.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
